  </div>

<p>I originally programmed the app with <a href="http://ai2.appinventor.mit.edu/">MIT App Inventor</a>, but then I decided to write it from scratch using Android Studio. If you‚Äôre an Android beginner, I would recommend you using the original app (<a href="http://ai2.appinventor.mit.edu/?galleryId=6532138936041472">released in the App Inventor gallery</a>), since it‚Äôs easier to program and to edit. Otherwise, the newer app can be found <a href="https://github.com/marcocipriani01/RoverBluetooth">on GitHub</a>.</p>

